Qxf4 11. Nxf4 Ne7 $1 (11... cxd4 $2 12. Bxf5 exf5 13. Nxd5 $16 {Gligoric}) (
11... g6 $2 12. dxc5 $1 Nd7 13. Bxf5 gxf5 14. Nd3 $16 {Gligoric}) 12. Be2 $1 h4
